OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C Following the glorious implementation 
OL,5,C of FARTS (Fully Autonomous Robotic    
OL,6,C Transport System), a minor logic      
OL,7,C divergence has occurred. Several      
OL,8,C thousand Snowmobiles have gone 'feral'
OL,9,C and are currently hiding in the       
OL,10,FCpermafrost to evade capture.          
OL,11,F                                       
