OL,13,F skilled trackers to capture and return
OL,14,F these traiterous machines for re-     
OL,15,F programming.                          
OL,16,                                       F
OL,17,  CITIZEN REWARDS:F                     
OL,18,F +50 Loyalty Rating per unit recovered.
OL,19,F Extra 500ml Kefir (Hero Blend)        
OL,20,F 1x voucher for Prodmash N12 borscht.  
OL,22,A]GPENALTY: Unauthorised harbouring of  
OL,23,A]GFARTS hardware is a Class A felony   
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
